{"tid":193741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"物理撚請入","createTime":"2017-04-09T13:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T00:56:24.000Z","uid":89955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9fabcdf4fa8e64775d36fe77b78cd8cd51895d3","tid":193741,"uid":89955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:27:49.000Z","msg":"地球轉得咁快<br />\n咁航拍機定係空中唔郁<br />\n係唔係會慢慢消失？？<br />\n<br />\n我地跟住地球轉因為我地痴住地面姐<br />\n咁d飛緊既雀呢？"},{"pid":"52dd00c7f8a57f1f548c0772b11c0d28c20ea8da","tid":193741,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:31:37.000Z","msg":"引力大到你會跟住佢轉"},{"pid":"3bc52354b8622611cf17e78e26c8167f14119dae","tid":193741,"uid":104776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:37:38.000Z","msg":"就算你喺天空<br />\n唔等於你就會可以擺脫gravitational pull<br />\n就算月球咁叉遠都有<br />\n<br />\n天空既gravitational field strength <br />\n同earth surface 基本上係一樣<br />\n都係9.81Nkg^-1"},{"pid":"6f880525213755fb0959a193cc68a68873b2065a","tid":193741,"uid":104776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:41:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算你喺天空<br />\n唔等於你就會可以擺脫gravitational pull<br />\n就算月球咁叉遠都有<br />\n<br />\n天空既gravitational field strength <br />\n同earth surface 基本上係一樣<br />\n都係9.81Nkg^-1</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講多句<br />\ngravity既range 係infinity <br />\n離開地球越遠 係個gravitational field strength 係愈嚟愈低 <br />\n但in definition <br />\n你去到宇宙既盡頭 地球都仲吸緊你"},{"pid":"7df25e45df0d5fdd7cc42cbdb4173de60f0df454","tid":193741,"uid":57526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:15:26.000Z","msg":"因爲你同埋個地球係同一個system 入面，Due to inertia，你既速度其實係同個地球同步轉緊，而又因為你既inertia frame of reference 係企係地球望上出，所以會覺得無郁<br />\n<br />\n利申：中學阿sir講+大學自己研究過，有錯請指正"},{"pid":"b57533682a92f17785e6270606b122bfd827e322","tid":193741,"uid":89955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T19:13:56.000Z","msg":"Gravity都係向下姐<br />\n而加我講緊橫向呀<br />\n咁我痴住地下向左/右郁<br />\n咁隻雀係空中又痴住d咩向左/右郁呀 如果你話佢跟住地球郁"},{"pid":"7cbdaf4e4823548588fd14cb480418708da6ef50","tid":193741,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T19:18:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Gravity都係向下姐<br />\n而加我講緊橫向呀<br />\n咁我痴住地下向左/右郁<br />\n咁隻雀係空中又痴住d咩向左/右郁呀 如果你話佢跟住地球郁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jype1tk8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjype1tk8&h=61b37831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個力向下都可以左右郁架"},{"pid":"4ba4948bd74ce284806792ad0aa19c4e6ce97019","tid":193741,"uid":89955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T19:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Gravity都係向下姐<br />\n而加我講緊橫向呀<br />\n咁我痴住地下向左/右郁<br />\n咁隻雀係空中又痴住d咩向左/右郁呀 如果你話佢跟住地球郁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jype1tk8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjype1tk8&h=61b37831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個力向下都可以左右郁架</blockquote><br />\n咁而加都無痴住地下 隻雀點左右郁"},{"pid":"295654c366f46328f7b2d498c37203ffd29c097d","tid":193741,"uid":68583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T19:46:56.000Z","msg":"首先 ，力可以拆做 x-y axis睇，前面個個ching個張圖，y-axis gravity 向下， x-axis向前， 造成net force(姐係轉圈)。 <br />\nNewton first law/ inertia 都可以解釋當一樣野keep 住向前 就會向前， 所以就算雀仔曉飛，佢都會keep住一道力同地球一樣速度咁轉。<br />\n第二，地球係有空氣， 你亦可以理解做雀仔就算飛緊， 都有空氣推緊佢。 雀仔拍翼產生既反作用力可以令佢轉向或者起飛。"},{"pid":"7318d275ac3b618feab21d65aa4e180fbec825b4","tid":193741,"uid":18664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T19:50:37.000Z","msg":"慣性啊, Inertia 啊屌"},{"pid":"7a1e5826b3456a93b75fb443b52f2b500d467ea1","tid":193741,"uid":55757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T20:09:50.000Z","msg":"屌 仲以為有咩高深嘅問題<br />\n點知又係依條月經題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己上網Google 下都大把答案啦"},{"pid":"6a73569fa21973990c732bdab4d18f7576c4403d","tid":193741,"uid":89955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:52:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先 ，力可以拆做 x-y axis睇，前面個個ching個張圖，y-axis gravity 向下， x-axis向前， 造成net force(姐係轉圈)。 <br />\nNewton first law/ inertia 都可以解釋當一樣野keep 住向前 就會向前， 所以就算雀仔曉飛，佢都會keep住一道力同地球一樣速度咁轉。<br />\n第二，地球係有空氣， 你亦可以理解做雀仔就算飛緊， 都有空氣推緊佢。 雀仔拍翼產生既反作用力可以令佢轉向或者起飛。</blockquote><br />\n咁即係你話隻雀move along y axis十個鐘再落地都係返起點啦 d空氣推佢?? 我唔是好信"},{"pid":"6f79bdef94ce33e86a4c0ca398ed20073d901748","tid":193741,"uid":89955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慣性啊, Inertia 啊屌</blockquote><br />\n慣你老母 慣幾耐呀 我撚知空氣推緊我"},{"pid":"3df5d898ae3024481f0df7fa9b3080489cbbc556","tid":193741,"uid":89955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:56:24.000Z","msg":"咁我企係地面究竟係空氣推下定地表推我定both<br />\n你地話空氣推雀仔呀嘛<br />\n咁人呢"}]}